findings.title: Mistyped argument names in functions
findings.description: The functions that allow to make changes on liquidityWallet, strategicSalesWallet, gameOperationsWallet, teamWallet, communityAirdropWallet, privateSaleWallet all make whitelist for marketingWallet.

findings.title: Loose timeLimit validation for sell transactions on pancakeSwap
findings.description: block.timestamp can be controlled by any users, which allows users to make transactions under the condition where block.timestamp = timeLimit + 24 * 1 hours. By that, users can sell the tokens without increasing maxSellPerDayLimit.

findings.title: Inefficient Function Declaration
findings.description: Functions without concrete specifiers are public by default, making it easier to catch incorrect assumptions about who can access the function.
